{"tid":2010201,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色服裝節 呼籲去黃店買衫 強化良心經濟","createTime":"2020-05-10T09:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T04:10:48.000Z","uid":240968,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d4b6f18cbe79e58d010042d632a107f5a988cb48","tid":2010201,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T09:17:40.000Z","msg":"講過好多次，黃色經濟圈唔止食店，仲有好多生活面向要香港人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。夏天就到，係時候買衫，你今年諗住去邊到買衫? 仲想去<span style=\"color: blue;\">IT/連鎖店</span>消費? No way! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年俾機會小店，<span style=\"color: gold;\">呼籲大家6月前去搵一間服裝店買衫褲</span>: 西裝/背心/裙/泳衣/手飾等等; 買咩都得! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家唔買下半年612之後可能日日發夢，到時無心情買~<br />\n<br />\n最重要係令自己熟悉邊到有合適自己服飾既黃店，買慣左就會keep住買。咁先成功擴大黃圈既力量! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之今個5月，買衫! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597930d6baf94d349a4db21d08e04a4c399fbdba","tid":2010201,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T09:18:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c48206b1bfa75fdb5c24968c0a717c8eddd6ab0e","tid":2010201,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T09:20:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb483503b565fe1f0714c627629655301ba39b15","tid":2010201,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T09:21:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd2d6058a7d8d3bf14220d4152f6613f53881000","tid":2010201,"uid":292497,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T09:22:42.000Z","msg":"有無男裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見親都係女裝<br />\n除左zuitable但我又唔著西裝"},{"pid":"9fc5ad371006d2fdfe0acf0c77ae66cc66822e58","tid":2010201,"uid":52342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T09:23:56.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n最好係休閑服<img src=\